<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idbcadf132-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original a reference to “this title” meaning title XIII of <ref href="/us/pl/90/448">Pub. L. 90–448</ref>, <date date="1968-08-01">Aug. 1, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/572">82 Stat. 572</ref>, known as the National Flood Insurance Act of 1968, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s4001">section 4001 of this title</ref> and Tables.</p>
</note>
